com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata

Interface IDetailEntry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDepthEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DetailEntry, InternalDepthEntry, InternalDetailEntry

    public interface IDetailEntry
    Standard interface supported by any object representing an entry in a market detail (unaggregated depth).

    • Method Detail

      • getID

        int getID()
        Unique ID associated with this entry.
        Returns:
        id associated with this entry.

      • getInstrument

        IInstrument getInstrument()
        Instrument associated with this entry.

        May be null if not yet assigned.

        Returns:
        Instrument associated with entry or null if unassigned.

      • getMarketDataItems

        IMarketDataItem[] getMarketDataItems()
        Gets all market data defined for this entry.

        The entire array should not be processed. Process until a null is encountered or an entry with fieldID == 0.

        Returns:
        Array of market data items associated with this entry. May be null.

      • getMarketDataItem

        IMarketDataItem getMarketDataItem(int fieldID)
        Returns the market data associated with the given field ID - see the FIELD constants in FieldInfos.
        Parameters:
        fieldID - ID of value.
        Returns:
        Market data item.

      • getPrice

        int getPrice()
        Price associated with this entry. Note that all prices are represented as whole numbers. Where a price has a fractional part, eg price is in dollars and cents, the value is the whole number of cents.
        Returns:
        the price

        Quantity

      • isBuy

        Is this a buy or sell side entry?
        Returns:

      • isEmpty

        Is this entry empty?
        Returns:
        true if empty
